<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وقرئت:</span> <span class="c2">(قَالَ فَالْحَقَّ وَالْحَقَّ أَقُولُ)</span> بنصبهما جميعاً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">فَمن رَفَع فعلى ضربين:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>على معنى فَأنا الحقُّ، والحقُّ أقُولُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>ويجوز رفْعُه علي معْنَى فَالحَقُّ مِنِّي.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>ومن نصب فعلى معنى فالحقَّ أَقُولُ والحقَّ لأملأن جهنم حَقًّا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>* * *<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(وَلَتَعْلَمُنَّ نَبَأَهُ بَعْدَ حِينٍ (٨٨)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>أي بعد الموت.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>